Duke Mitchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Duke_Mitchell 0 Duke Mitchell (May 9, 1926 – December 2, 1981) was an American film actor, slapstick comedian, crooner and independent film director of 1970s gangster movies starring himself. Mitchell often performed his nightclub act in and around Palm Springs, California and anointed himself the "King of Palm Springs."
